leadership.

289
00:16:05,507 --> 00:16:07,146
All right, we need
to make a shift.

290
00:16:07,266 --> 00:16:08,435
Bagwell, I'm telling you
right now,

291
00:16:08,555 --> 00:16:10,316
If I make my play
and you go soft,

292
00:16:10,436 --> 00:16:12,043
I will sail you off
that loft balcony

293
