And no one will bat an eye.

294
00:16:13,574 --> 00:16:15,282
My aim is true, Don.

295
00:16:15,402 --> 00:16:16,345
Keep it in your pants.

296
00:16:16,465 --> 00:16:19,288
I'll keep it in
my pants, all right?

297
00:16:19,408 --> 00:16:22,789
All right, all in favor of
changing the regime, say "Aye."

298
00:16:22,909 --> 00:16:23,817
Aye, aye, Captain.

