Might have worked when
you were stealing gumballs,

343
00:18:11,158 --> 00:18:13,477
But our asses are
on the line now, okay?

344
00:18:13,597 --> 00:18:15,062
And we all have deals
with the General.

345
00:18:15,182 --> 00:18:16,978
So that's the way
it's gonna be.

346
00:18:17,098 --> 00:18:19,973
And if you notice,
even Gretchen hasn't
leapt to your defense.

347
00:18:20,093 --> 00:18:21,854
Linc, just let him wear
his crown.

348
