I would if I thought he wasn't
gonna sell this thing.

349
00:18:24,064 --> 00:18:25,790
Oh, what, am I the only one
who's thought about that?

350
00:18:25,910 --> 00:18:27,305
Look, here's the
deal, Linc.

351
00:18:27,425 --> 00:18:28,855
At some point,
you'll have a vote.

352
00:18:28,975 --> 00:18:30,074
But until then,
you're done, all right?

353
00:18:30,194 --> 00:18:31,119
We're shuttin' you down, okay?

354
00:18:31,239 --> 00:18:32,887
You're no longer in charge.

355
00:18:40,372 --> 00:18:43,003
GRETCHEN:
Uh-Oh, looks like
there's been a recount.

356
00:18:43,123 --> 00:18:44,379
Bad time?

357
00:18:44,499 --> 00:18:47,061
No, perfect.

358
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:52,286
The second you stop

359
00:18:52,406 --> 00:18:54,689
Doing what I tell you to do,

360
00:18:54,809 --> 00:18:57,478
I'm gonna blow your brains out.

361
00:19:09,998 --> 00:19:11,618
Bring her back.

362
00:19:11,738 --> 00:19:13,606
It's not gonna be
the same.

363
00:19:15,048 --> 00:19:16,409
Stir any memories?

364
00:19:20,448 --> 00:19:25,818
I was ten. We were on a camping
trip in Jackson Hole.

365
00:19:25,886 --> 00:19:28,288
Fishing, hiking.

366
00:19:28,355 --> 00:19:30,619
Family huddled under a blanket
in front of the bonfire.

367
00:19:30,739 --> 00:19:32,058
You can stop now.

368
00:19:32,126 --> 00:19:34,327
Why? Because two years later
it was gone?

369
00:19:34,395 --> 00:19:37,664
You know, three
of the four

370
00:19:37,731 --> 00:19:39,365
People in this photograph
are still alive.

371
00:19:39,433 --> 00:19:40,967
So what are you
suggesting,

372
00:19:41,035 --> 00:19:42,735
Grab my fishing pole?

373
00:19:42,803 --> 00:19:44,070
Time for a...

374
00:19:44,138 --> 00:19:45,905
A family reunion in Wyoming?

375
00:19:45,973 --> 00:19:48,041
Or wherever you like.

376
00:19:48,108 --> 00:19:50,877
Don't tell me it's something
you haven't wished for.

377
00:19:50,945 --> 00:19:55,181
I wished for a lot
of unrealistic things.

378
00:19:55,249 --> 00:19:57,450
I got over them, too.

379
00:19:57,518 --> 00:19:58,885
Why,

380
00:19:58,953 --> 00:20:01,754
When we can make this happen?

381
00:20:03,457 --> 00:20:07,493
These pictures could have been
taken anywhere at any time.

382
00:20:08,343 --> 00:20:09,876
Before you were incarcerated,

383
00:20:09,996 --> 00:20:11,492
You'd go to visit her grave
on the anniversary

384
00:20:11,612 --> 00:20:13,132
Of her funeral.
All right, enough.

385
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,599
You'd bring a bouquet
of blue irises.

386
00:20:14,719 --> 00:20:15,902
You'd sit for an hour.

387
00:20:15,970 --> 00:20:16,786
I said stop it.

388
00:20:16,906 --> 00:20:17,957
When you'd leave,
you'd take a flower

389
00:20:18,077 --> 00:20:19,155
And pin it to your lapel.

390
00:20:19,275 --> 00:20:20,743
She watched you
do this every year.

391
00:20:20,863 --> 00:20:21,997
She's seen the pain you carry.

392
00:20:22,117 --> 00:20:22,945
She wants
to make amends.

393
00:20:23,065 --> 00:20:24,577
All right!

394
00:20:26,013 --> 00:20:29,048
So you did a little digging.
Good for you.

395
00:20:29,116 --> 00:20:31,017
But everything out of your mouth
is a lie,

396
00:20:31,085 --> 00:20:32,785
And I don't believe a word
of it.

397
00:20:34,113 --> 00:20:36,022
So let's just stop.

