00:21:10,724 --> 00:21:12,492
If he's working with someone
from the Company,

412
00:21:12,559 --> 00:21:14,927
They wouldn't want their names
on any flight manifests.

413
00:21:14,995 --> 00:21:16,362
All right, they're trying
to get Scylla

414
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:17,764
Out of the country
by boat undetected.

415
00:21:17,831 --> 00:21:19,732
Let's go.

416
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:21,334
Alex,
Yeah?

417
00:21:21,402 --> 00:21:24,437
Thanks for coming
when you did, man.

418
00:21:24,505 --> 00:21:29,208
You helped me like you said
you would. I owe you.

419
00:22:14,221 --> 00:22:15,722
SELF:
Okay, I'll do
the talking.

420
00:22:15,789 --> 00:22:16,537
You guys wait here.

421
00:22:16,657 --> 00:22:18,758
Alex, let's go.

422
00:22:22,796 --> 00:22:23,896
Afternoon.

423
00:22:23,964 --> 00:22:25,164
How's it going?

424
00:22:25,232 --> 00:22:26,899
What can I do you for?

425
00:22:26,967 --> 00:22:27,834
Recognize her?

426
00:22:27,901 --> 00:22:29,702
SELF:
Her name's Tia Hayden.

427
00:22:29,770 --> 00:22:32,005
Can't say I do.
Wish I did.

428
00:22:32,072 --> 00:22:33,473
Nice little tomato there.

