you were talking about.

447
00:23:09,143 --> 00:23:11,582
He wanted to know which berth a
private charter was docking in.

448
00:23:11,702 --> 00:23:14,013
He asked me to move it further
down the dock, which I did.

449
00:23:14,081 --> 00:23:15,692
Further away
from the Coast Guard slip?

450
00:23:15,812 --> 00:23:18,518
I didn't ask.
And I didn't accept any money.

451
00:23:18,585 --> 00:23:19,900
If he said he paid me,
he's lying.

452
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:21,754
What's the point of departure?

453
00:23:21,822 --> 00:23:23,556
Nassau, Bahamas. Round trip.

454
00:23:23,624 --> 00:23:24,891
When does it arrive?

455
00:23:24,959 --> 00:23:27,593
Arrived.

456
00:23:29,663 --> 00:23:32,365
Hey, everybody!
Okay, my name is Don Self!

457
00:23:32,433 --> 00:23:34,400
Homeland Security.

458
00:23:34,468 --> 00:23:38,237
My colleagues and I are hoping
that you guys have a wonderful

459
00:23:38,305 --> 00:23:40,640
And safe trip.
Unfortunately,

460
00:23:40,708 --> 00:23:44,077
We're going to have to do
a quick luggage check search.

