playing you, Doctor,

499
00:25:57,177 --> 00:25:59,512
You'll get the same lobotomy
as Scofield.

500
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:03,082
Just get it done.

501
00:26:40,454 --> 00:26:41,454
Go!

502
00:27:11,098 --> 00:27:13,032
If you fight
when those cuffs are off,

503
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:14,600
The guards will stomp the life
out of you.

504
00:27:14,668 --> 00:27:17,537
Yeah.

505
00:27:22,876 --> 00:27:24,344
Forgive
the dramatics.

506
00:27:24,411 --> 00:27:26,446
