507
00:27:26,513 --> 00:27:28,781
<i>You are the Company.
You're his daughter.</i>

508
00:27:28,849 --> 00:27:30,249
Do you want
to find Michael Scofield?

509
00:27:30,317 --> 00:27:31,618
Of course I do.

510
00:27:35,356 --> 00:27:37,023
It's 60 miles northeast

511
00:27:37,091 --> 00:27:39,192
